        "提示：前往写有下面命题的门后解锁\nisProp、isSet、isContr：\nPx:True,Py:True,(x=y)~=True": "Hint: Go past the gate\nbearing the following theorem\nto unlock isProp, isSet, and isContr:\nPx:True,Py:True,(x=y)~=True",
        "解锁命题截断类型“[[”...“]]”\n它强制把类型变成命题": "Unlock the propositional truncation type\n\"[[\" ... \"]]\"\nIt forcibly turns a type\ninto a proposition",
        "当类型是纯命题时\n类型等价终于跟\n逻辑等价一样了": "When a type is a mere proposition\ntype equivalence finally becomes\nthe same as logical equivalence",
