        "证明思路：将所有满足f(x)=y\n的数对(x,y)利用\nnatXnat=nat的构造\n编码成单个自然数": "Proof idea: Encode every pair (x,y)\nsatisfying f(x)=y\ninto a single natural number\nusing the construction\nnatXnat=nat",
