        "解锁Option类型": "Unlock the Option type",
        "请定义一个函数fillList :\nPa:U,Px:a,Pn:nat,List a\n它输出n个x组成的列表\n如：fillList Bool 1b 2\n === cons 1b (cons 1b nil)\n#t:=": "Please define a function fillList :\nPa:U,Px:a,Pn:nat,List a\nIt outputs a list consisting of n copies of x\nFor example:\nfillList Bool 1b 2\n === cons 1b (cons 1b nil)\n#t:=",
        "请定义一个函数lastList :\nPa:U,Pl:List a,Option a\n若列表非空则输出\n最后一个放入的值some x\n若列表为nil则输出none\n如 lastList Bool\n(cons 1b (cons 0b nil))\n === some 1b\n#t:=": "Please define a function lastList :\nPa:U,Pl:List a,Option a\nIf the list is non-empty\noutput the last inserted value some x\nIf the list is nil\noutput none\nFor example, lastList Bool\n(cons 1b (cons 0b nil))\n === some 1b\n#t:=",
        "请定义一个函数firstList :\nPa:U,Pl:List a,Option a\n若列表非空则输出\n第一个放入的值some x\n若列表为nil则输出none\n如 firstList Bool\n(cons 1b (cons 0b nil))\n === some 0b\n#t:=": "Please define a function firstList :\nPa:U,Pl:List a,Option a\nIf the list is non-empty\noutput the first inserted value some x\nIf the list is nil\noutput none\nFor example, firstList Bool\n(cons 1b (cons 0b nil))\n === some 0b\n#t:=",
