        "请定义一个函数sumList :\n(List nat)->nat\n对列表的所有元素求和\n如sumList (cons 1 (cons 2 (cons 3 nil)))\n === 6\n#t:=": "Please define a function sumList :\n(List nat)->nat\nwhich sums all elements of the list\nFor example,\nsumList (cons 1 (cons 2 (cons 3 nil)))\n === 6\n#t:=",
        "请定义一个函数mapList :\nPa:U,Pb:U,Pf:a->b,List a->List b\n通过函数f把List a中的元素\n一一映射构造List b\n如mapList (List nat) nat sumList\n(cons nil (cons (cons 3 nil) nil))\n === cons 0 (cons 3 nil)\n#t:=": "Please define a function mapList :\nPa:U,Pb:U,Pf:a->b,List a->List b\nwhich maps each element of List a\nthrough function f\nto construct a List b\nFor example,\nmapList (List nat) nat sumList\n(cons nil (cons (cons 3 nil) nil))\n === cons 0 (cons 3 nil)\n#t:=",
